1407
01:10:36,149 --> 01:10:37,651
Tu regalo de bodas.

1408
01:10:37,900 --> 01:10:40,278
Es tu regalo de bodas, cariño.

1409
01:10:42,739 --> 01:10:44,116
¿En serio?

1410
01:10:44,741 --> 01:10:45,833
