Estoy hablando de Giorgio Armani,
Gianni Versace, Coco Chanel...

1632
01:21:13,118 --> 01:21:14,415
<i>...Y ves Sam Laurent.</i>

1633
01:21:15,079 --> 01:21:16,706
Steve, ven un segundo.

1634
01:21:16,914 --> 01:21:18,712
